summary: Standalone retexture of Ashara Princess of the Woods
descriptionHtml:
Ranger of the Woods by Tru3Magic
Original Mod Author - [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/259193]SydneyB[/url]

--------------------------------------------------------
Description:

Simple STANDALONE (you don\'t need the original mod) retexture of [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18008]Ashara Princess of the Woods[/url]

Includes:
- Bodice
- Bracers
- Belt
- Fur skirt
- Boots

At this moment comes in one color.

You can buy whole set in Drunken Huntsman inside Whiterun.

Critique, suggestions and advice is always welcome!

Don\'t forget to endorse if you like it!

Enjoy! :)

--------------------------------------------------------
Installation/Uninstallation

I recommend use NMM.
